wikipedia_page.main: George Moleski (born 27 July 1987) is an English retired semi-professional footballer who made one appearance in the Football League for Brentford as a midfielder.

response: Watts made his first appearance of the 2005–06 season in a 5–0 League Cup defeat at Cheltenham Town on 23 August 2005, replacing Paul Brooker after 74 minutes. He made another appearance in a Football League Trophy first round shootout defeat to Oxford United on 18 October, replacing George Moleski (who in turn had replaced Eddie Hutchinson during the first half) during extra time. Watts was not called into the first team again and was released in June 2006. He made three appearances during his time with the Bees.
